<p>WSJ: You watch physics lectures and Harlem Globetrotters [on YouTube]?
</p> <p>Gates: This social-networking thing takes you to crazy places.
</p> <p>WSJ: But those were stolen, correct?
</p> <p>Gates: Stolen's a strong word. It's copyrighted content that the owner wasn't paid for. So yes."</p>
